dct_title_s: Brisbane and region : easy to use, CBD map, suburban map, regional map, rail map, ferry map, postcodes, points of interest, fully indexed
dct_description_sm: Cover title. Maps of "Brisbane region" and "Brisbane suburbs" show radial distances from downtown Brisbane. Includes indexes and col. ill. Ancillary maps: Brisbane ferry map; Brisbane rail network. Recto: Brisbane region.
dct_publisher_sm: Eighty Mile Plains, Qld : Hema Maps Pty Ltd., 2007.
